# üß© PCB Design Roadmap

This roadmap covers all essential topics for learning PCB (Printed Circuit Board) design from absolute beginner to advanced. Use this as a checklist or syllabus to guide your learning journey.

---
Here are some high-quality, **free video resources** for learning PCB design from beginner to advanced:

---

### üü¢ YouTube Channels & Playlists

- [PCB Design Tutorial for Beginners (PCBWay)](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7bYl-Y6wC6JQFzW6XcUeGp9Q6bqvPZtL)  
  Covers basics of PCB design, schematic creation, and layout using various software.

- [KiCad Like a Pro (Contextual Electronics)](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLnGqih5ozY3pAqOqF0O8pSnfwmk-1AgGg)  
  Step-by-step KiCad tutorials for beginners.

- [PCB Design with Altium Designer (Altium)](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQK4Z6n6M5UeNQvM9PXjVvnbO7M8JwK4k)  
  Comprehensive guide to using Altium Designer for PCB layout.

- [PCB Design for Beginners (GreatScott!)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QK6a3gSw-6I)  
  Basic concepts of PCB design, manufacturing, and assembly.

- [PCB Design Tutorials (EEVblog)](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLv4viiJ6lKVjfJQ0wJJ8X6qG9Vq0vyZ6U)  
  Industry insights and hands-on tutorials from a professional electronics engineer.

